ll\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">257 &quot;/ home / ixdba / ftp_data&quot; created</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">ftp&gt;? (enter &quot;?&quot; to display the ftp command line executable for all orders)</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">Commands may be abbreviated. Commands are:</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">! Cr mdir proxy send</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">$ Delete mget sendport site</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">account debug mkdir put size</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">append dir mls pwd status</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">ascii disconnect mode quit struct</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">bell form modtime quote system</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">binary get mput recv sunique</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">bye glob newer reget tenex</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">case hash nmap rstatus trace</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">ccc help nlist rhelp type</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">cd idle ntrans rename user</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">cdup image open reset umask</span></span> </div><div> <span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">chmod lcd passive restart verbose