an> </p><p> <span>mysql-uroot-p - default-character-set = utf8 wapad &lt;dd.sql <br /><br /> mysqldump-u root-p-c - default-character-set = latin1 wap_resdb downlog_bak&gt; downlog_bak.sql <br /> mysqldump-u root-p-c - default-character-set = latin1 wap_resdb downlog_month&gt; downlog_month.sql <br /> mysqldump-u root-p-c - default-character-set = latin1 wap_resdb haoduan&gt; haoduan.sql</span> </p><p></p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','solution is very simple mysqldump import, export, when the character set specified on the line.  mysqldump-u root-p-c - default-character-set = utf-8 wapad site> dd.sqlmysql-uroot-p - default-character-set = utf8 wapad <dd.sql  mysqldump-u root-p-c - default-character-set = latin1 wap_resdb...'),(120,'Mysql','Database','en','/a/db/mysql/2010/0422/52.html','http://www.ixdba.net',' Today, R & D personnel in the...','_Today_R__D_personnel_in_the','2010-04-22','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> Today, R &amp; D personnel in the debug java program, found the mysql quoted the following problems: </p><p> java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Packet is larger than max_allowed_packet from server configuration of 1048576 bytes </p><p> at org.gjt.mm.mysql.Buffer.ensureCapacity (Buffer.java: 398) </p><p> at org.gjt.mm.mysql.Buffer.writeBytesNoNull (Buffer.java: 386) </p><p> at org.gjt.mm.mysql.PreparedStatement.executeUpdate (PreparedStatement.java: 352) </p><p> at com.cicro.cws.database.DBManager.execute (DBManager.java: 450) </p><p> at com.cicro.cws.publish.PreparePublish.saveSiteInstanceXmlIntoDB (PreparePublish.java: 827) </p><p> at com.cicro.cws.publish.PreparePublish.generatePublishFiles (PreparePublish.java: 181) </p><p> at com.cicro.cws.publish.PublishManager.publish (PublishManager.java: 180) </p><p> at com.cicro.cws.synchronize.InstanceSynchronize.publishSite (InstanceSynchronize.java: 954) </p><p> at com.cicro.cws.site.Site.publish (Site.java: 365) </p><p> at com.cicro.cws.site.Site.run (Site.java: 338) </p><p> at java.lang.Thread.run (Thread.java: 536) </p><p></p><p> Resolve as follows: </p><p> This problem is due to import sql file is larger than the system default value of max_allowed_packet, the solution: for example, modify the increase in the my.cnf: max_allowed_packet = 32M # or higher, of course, can also join the mysqld startup parameters, but This variable must restart mysqld effect when it is loaded, it must restart mysqld! </p><p> I loaded the max_allowed_packet parameter to mysqld in the mysql startup file, mysqld file some settings are as follows: </p><p> $ {MYSQL} / bin / mysqld - user = mysql - datadir = $ {MYSQL} / data &quot;$ @&quot; \\ </p><p> - Language = $ {MYSQL} / share / mysql / english-O max_connections = 500-O wait_timeout = 600 \\ </p><p> -O key_buffer = 32M - max_allowed_packet = 32M - port = $ {port} - socket = / tmp / mysql.sock &amp; </p><p></p><p> One - max_allowed_packet = 32M must sign in front of DD. </p><p></p><p> Some information about the max_allowed_packet: </p><p> Many MySQL programs have some internal variables can be set at run time. Process variable settings and other long option with the same value. </p><p> For example, mysql has a max_allowed_packet variable, you can control the maximum length of its communication buffer. Mysql will want to set the value of max_allowed_packet variable 16MB, use any of the following command: </p><p> shell&gt; mysql - max_allowed_packet = 16777216 </p><p> shell&gt; mysql - max_allowed_packet = 16M </p><p> 1 byte command to the specified value. 2 command specify a value in megabytes. Variable values can have a suffix of K, M or G (for uppercase or lowercase) to indicate kilobytes, megabytes or gigabytes of units. </p><p> In the options file, the variable setting does not guide the dash: </p><p> [Mysql] </p><p> max_allowed_packet = 16777216 </p><p> Or: </p><p> [Mysql] </p><p> max_allowed_packet = 16M </p><p> If you like the underscore variable name can be a dash. </p><p> Note: max_allowed_packet parameter is only after the mysql4, in mysql4 previous versions, this parameter has not </p><p> In addition, you can also be / etc / my.cnf file to increase in the my.cnf to set max_allowed_packet = 16M, then restart mysql also. As for the acquisition of my.cnf, mysql home directory from the support-files through the change template by. <br /></p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>',' Today, R & D personnel in the debug java program, found the mysql quoted the following problems:  java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Packet is larger than max_allowed_packet from server configuration of 1048576 bytes  at org.gjt.mm.mysql.Buffer.ensureCapacity (Buffer.java: 398)  at...'),(121,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/1026/801.html','http://www.ixdba.net','As a member of the Apache...','As_a_member_of_the_Apache','2010-10-26','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">As a member of the Apache Software Foundation, I tend to support the position of open source software license agreements more freely, such as Apache License (v2.0), BSD, or MIT license agreement. I firmly believe that businesses should be encouraged to use open source software, so that they can use open source software to do anything they want, as much as possible in the current legal framework of the relaxation of restrictions. Liberal free software license agreement allows the software development community to do better. Free and open source software development to encourage genuine, attentive, and the strength of the volunteer activities of participants as &quot;open heart&quot; campaign, as the software companies can sell services and &quot;enterprise-class software functionality,&quot; and do not change into a single individual to master all the important rights of software.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">I have to honest - I\'m not very keen on the Java language - I prefer to use Python, Javascript, C, C + +, PHP and even write a program, but I found that Java is everywhere, I fell. Java and the JVM has now become my team developed Cloudkick in the core of many components, but no replacement.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Today IBM announced the need to shift their focus to shift to develop based on OpenJDK. This is the Oracle infringement against Google\'s Android, after another major event. Oracle is a big company specializes in playing the political company, specializes in the extraction of value - I am sure he will extract from the Sun of the shell in the last dime out of date.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">When the Sun, is now Oracle, the OpenJDK when placed under the GPL license, TCK license agreement problem has been hanging more than 5 years. Some blog on this issue in-depth introduction to [1] [2] [3], I suggest everyone TCK, Apache and Sun should be more between the stories to find out - but this is not my concern here.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">I think he is an advocate of open source software, though with some people, such as Richard Stallman - GNU\'s founder, the approach is different. Richard\'s point of view on many issues with me are not very consistent, but one thing is consistent, Java world, the phenomenon of more and more chaotic that I began license agreement for software platforms and beliefs to change.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">6 years ago, Richard made a &quot;free but with a yoke - Java trap.&quot; At that time I do not agree that moral arguments about software freedom, but now I believe, Java platform is a trap.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">In his article, Richard talked about &quot;free software world,&quot; and a lot of other GNU projects, one of which I find very important: If your application relies on a platform, you will be the platform of the license agreement and the development process constraints.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Any software, any language will encounter this problem. For example, if a free run only on Microsoft\'s Windows operating system that still need to pay for the free world. However, in GUN / Linux software running as dependent on other non-free software, it is equally meaningless. In the past, Motif (before the LessTif) and Qt (the developers to its free before) the major problems are arising in this regard. Most 3D graphics are dependent on non-free driver, also have this problem. But now, the biggest problem has come from Java, because the development of free software Java people are great feeling. The attractiveness of the language deceived them, they ignore the issue of independence, fall into the Java trap.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">If you develop software on Java and the JVM, you trapped in a company by - Oracle control of a single platform. Oracle to maintain control of the platform and refused to remove the TCK in the terms of use, effectively blocked the Apache Harmony project has not officially released. The lawsuit against Google over the obsession with the Oracle on the platform control.</span></span> </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','As a member of the Apache Software Foundation, I tend to support the position of open source software license agreements more freely, such as Apache License (v2.0), BSD, or MIT license agreement. I firmly believe that businesses should be encouraged to use open source software, so that they can use...'),(122,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/1026/800.html','http://www.ixdba.net','After 80 days after the...','After_80_days_after_the','2010-10-26','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">After 80 days after the development, Linus Torvalds released the Linux 2.6.36 version. It has a name &quot;fanged carnivorous bat&quot;; from the name on his way home from Torvalds get inspiration. New Linux kernel better than the previous version of it big - this is a rare thing, because in the past few years, the main development branch in each new version of the kernel source distribution has grown to hundreds of thousands of lines.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><br /> Kernels do not grow in size, because the developer carefully streamlined the default configuration file. However, the other patches to bring a wealth of new source code so 2.6.36 can provide a wealth of new features significantly - say, the controversial AppArmor Anquan development, a new memory Wai (OOM) end of the process device, the kernel thread improved, the basic Xen Dom0 support, and many file systems and virtual file system related optimization. Kernel hackers have also repaired a virtual machine system of one of them can cause some systems to write to the file storage medium slow slow unbearable bug. Other changes are expected by improving the response time of the system seems faster. As before, this new version also includes many new and improved drive - for example, for the Nouveau driver NVIDIA graphics chips now support the use of the recently out of the GeForce graphics cards on the Fermi chip. Kernel hackers as well to improve on the infrared remote control and receiver support.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><br /> The following provides a 2.6.36 kernel records brought more and more an overview of new features. This change will be issued with the Linux distribution with 2.6.36 kernel or later, and ultimately affect all Linux users, and allow end users to effectively feel the improvement. Finally, the kernel records also a glimpse into the 2.6.37 kernel version that will be some new directions.</span></span> </p><p> <strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">The kernel update has the following highlights:</span></span></strong> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Tilera processor architecture support. <br /> New file notification interface to fanotify. <br /> Intel graphics cards to achieve the integration of KMS and the KDB. <br /> Parallel management of the queue. <br /> Intel i3 / 5 platform, built-in smart card and the CPU power management. <br /> CIFS file system, the local cache. <br /> Virtual memory hierarchy to improve and enhance the desktop operating speed of response. <br /> To improve the virtual memory overflow terminator algorithms. <br /> AppArmor security model integrated (note: SELinux file-based tagging different, AppArmor is based on the path.)</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Download: <a href=\"http://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v2.6/linux-2.6.36.tar.bz2\">http://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v2.6/linux-2.6.36.tar.bz2</a></span></span> </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>','After 80 days after the development, Linus Torvalds released the Linux 2.6.36 version. It has a name \"fanged carnivorous bat\"; from the name on his way home from Torvalds get inspiration. New Linux kernel better than the previous version of it big - this is a rare thing, because in the past few...'),(123,'IT','IT','en','/a/IT/2010/1017/799.html','http://www.ixdba.net','IT sector as one of the few...','IT_sector_as_one_of_the_few','2010-10-17','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">IT sector as one of the few remaining myths, UNIX history of the development history of the development as a nation, full of ups and downs and struggle. It turned out to 70-80 years to the 20th century, almost all of the most significant invention of the computer, the great business stories, and other commercial open source movement closely linked to the war, witnessed a period of IT industry and a legend. <br /><br /> In 1969, Ken Thompson of Bell Labs to his beloved game to develop a new operating environment, and Dennis Ritchie to design a set of operating system called UNICS (later homonym taken as &quot;UNIX&quot;). R &amp; D results in this casual, but the computer field has opened up dramatically in the new world. <br /><br /> In the course of development of UNIX in the past forty years, never stopped crowded situation. Which last for decades between the two giants of war, as the industry made an indelible contribution. Today, customers are going to review IT is such a history has been settled, from the brilliant to the bottom, from the equal strength to the great disparities between the success or failure in that study. <br /><br /> Two giants, two peak showdown <br /><br /> If the IT industry in 2009 to make a ranking event occurs, then the &quot;big S&quot; the company was acquired events, will be able to squeeze into the top three. &quot;Big S&quot; which was once only in Silicon Valley with the &quot;Big I&quot; standing shoulder to shoulder of giants, and now the setting sun, had to make people regret the ever-changing shopping contest. What kind of events completely changed the &quot;Big S&quot; development path? What kind of competition is completely defeated &quot;Big S&quot; line of defense? <br /><br /> The first battle - UNIX separatist war <br /><br /> Early 80s, the face of fast-growing IT market in the computer information industry vendors, in pursuit of product differentiation and added value, have improved UNIX, derived from a variety of commercial UNIX versions, fully started the UNIX market battle . <br /><br /> In 1982, the station started the &quot;Big S&quot; ascended the stage of history. Derived from the UNIX operating system version of the introduction to the Java programming language and J2EE (Java2EnerpriseEdition) application platform launched, &quot;Big S&quot; greatly contributed to the development of business applications. Improved through continuous updates, the company\'s Solaris operating system has made considerable progress can be broad support for UNIX-based business applications. Meanwhile, the firm\'s market share, R &amp; D investment in time, well-trained staff, excellent business advice, so that the &quot;Big S&quot; made a brilliant market performance, becoming the most dynamic UNIX commercial manufacturers. However, as the most promising one of the commercial versions of UNIX, Solaris itself brought poor standard software, the optional and very expensive package, which affect the company\'s future development as a major drawback. <br /><br /> January 1986, &quot;Big I&quot; the birth of the company\'s AIX operating system. Since then, it take up a UNIX server platform to create the task, has become a &quot;Big I&quot; open systems and standards for companies to enter the world of the catalyst. With the continuing escalation of AIX version, which gradually version of Java2 support, and provide improved tools for load management applications, in business and government sectors to show their talents. Meanwhile, AIX performance in terms of security but also reputation, AIX4.3 became the first TCSECC2 the U.S. National Security Agency and the German Information Technology Security Certification Authority E3F-C2-certified 64-bit UNIX systems, the field in the UNIX market performance extraordinary. And &quot;Big S&quot; than the company\'s Solaris, AIX has a large database and development tools, the user can choose in addition to the existing application software can also be developed according to their needs, which is the &quot;big I&quot; company is a major lead, but also to promote sustainable and stable development of its future an important factor. <br /><br /> Especially noteworthy is the highlight AIX powerful is a landmark event. May 11, 1997, 4:50, world chess champion Garry Kasparov in with one called &quot;Deep Blue&quot; supercomputer through six innings against, the final hand over to concede defeat. The claims of the most intelligent person, Bureau of 2.5 pairs of 2.5 in the first five cases tie, deciding game in the sixth disc only 19 steps away to defeat at the hands of blue. This station is running the computer Deep Blue was the best commercial UNIX operating system - &quot;Big I&quot; of the AIX. <br /><br /> Battle in the UNIX market, the &quot;Big S&quot; a rapid response to make it to seize the opportunities, even in the &quot;Big I&quot; catch up time, still can not shake the &quot;Big S&quot; a brilliant performance, both through the eventual realization of a separatist war in the market to keep pace.</span></span> </p><p> <span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">The second confrontation - Processor Dispute <br /><br /> However, in the processors, the face of &quot;Big I&quot; strong technical innovation, &quot;Big S&quot; did not effectively countered the decline of the future foreshadowed. Whether to firmly grasp the leading edge of technological innovation, and has sufficient capital support, the business of winning opponents. <br /><br /> 80 20th century, is RISC (reduced instruction set computer) processor era. In 1984, the &quot;Big S&quot; of the SPARC architecture proposed; 1987, the first SPARC processor come out and quickly capture the market, to help the &quot;big S&quot; exceeded 10 billion revenue mark; in 1995, 64 UltraSPARCI the company microprocessor technology to achieve a qualitative leap; 1999, was a great success of the UltraSPARC-III, a &quot;Big S&quot; a milestone in the history of the microprocessor; 2005, 8-core 32-thread UltraSPARC-T1 launched; 2008 -2009, the 16-core &quot;Rock&quot; Ship Even Sank, this after 5 years, invested billions of dollars of products in the development process has some serious performance issues. Continuous deficit for the &quot;big S&quot; inability to continue to afford the high development costs, the outcome of the acquisition, but also to the future of this product has become more complicated and confusing. <br /><br /> In 1980, the &quot;Big I&quot; invented a prototype based on RISC architecture, microprocessor architecture to create a new heaven and earth; 1990, the &quot;Big I&quot; launched a RISC-based systems POWER1, officially opened the Power family genealogy brilliant prelude , since each generation of Power processors have created amazing success, has been at the pinnacle of processors. In 1997, the POWER2 architecture based on &quot;Deep Blue&quot; computer made the victory of man-machine war, is considered a milestone in the history of computer development; 1998, POWER3 processor and the subsequent update, the speed of the processor frequency shine ; 2001, &quot;Big I&quot; am the history of mankind\'s first dual-core processor POWER4; 2007Ã¥Â¹Â´, POWER6 processor performance and unparalleled speed, technical lead of 2-3 years into the processor market Pioneer; 2010, POWER78 core processors debut as a beautiful dawn, in the number of cores, chip design, operation speed, performance and other aspects of the work demonstrated an unrivaled advantage. <br /><br /> And &quot;Big S&quot; than the company\'s SPARC processor, &quot;Big I&quot; the company\'s POWER processors have no king to shake the status of the technology. With the industry\'s most robust product development roadmap, continuous research and development, advancing with a powerful innovation, &quot;Big I&quot; continue to inject fresh blood into the server market, to fully protect your investment, overall achievements in technology, performance and market leadership position. Processors, the war, the decisive opened the distance between the two giants, the &quot;Big S&quot; from glory into the bottom. <br /><br /> Fallen star, is lost to technology or capital loss? <br /><br /> SPARC twenty-five years of ups and downs, laid the &quot;Big S&quot; in the high-end microprocessor market leader, however, focusing as much on high-end server hardware and software development of the &quot;behind closed doors&quot; strategy, as well as hardware products are daily necessities of the trend, but as always, the standard of sales and production based on traditional general-purpose servers, the &quot;Big S&quot; has separated itself from the trend of industrial development, missed a good opportunity for development. Meanwhile, the high R &amp; D investment and market performance unsatisfactory, but also the &quot;big S&quot; the two most troublesome issues. <br /><br /> Recalling the most glorious era, in September 2000, &quot;Big S&quot; in the stock price close to 260 dollars, but the advanced information technology company in a very long period of time are not aware of the need with the times, when the elephants learn to dance &quot;Big I&quot; has an annual turnover of billions of dollars into the threshold, the &quot;Big S&quot; but with billions of dollars in market value of the club further away. In the financial crisis, business difficulties, large fund companies to sell shares under the influence of multiple factors such as, &quot;Big S&quot; performance gradually decline and eventually become a takeover target. Compete with the capital markets, technology sometimes have to yield to capital, because technological innovation can not do without the support of the capital. <br /><br /> Founded in 1982, was acquired in 2009, with the former glory, &quot;Big S&quot; slowly fade out of sight. In the future, &quot;Big S&quot; in the hardware business will go from here? Face the loss of personnel and their customers, &quot;Big S&quot; turn Zuoheganxiang? Regardless of whether the problem is 